imer, sier hun.", "N\u00e5 skal Sivilforsvaret ta stilling til om alenemoren f\u00e5r generelt tjenestefritak og dermed slipper \u00e5 bli innkalt igjen."]}, {"field": "category0", "value": "nyheter"}, {"field": "category1", "value": "nyheter|trondheim"}, {"field": "contenthash", "value": "3a5376018fb173897b21f76213c09599870141fdb0ab8e2ac30d607c43d5b76f"}, {"field": "createtime", "value": "2017-01-23T19:24:31.000Z"}, {"field": "description", "value": "Alenemoren Cecilie S\u00e6ther risikerte \u00e5 tape 15 000 kr p\u00e5 tjeneste i Sivilforsvaret. F\u00f8rst da justisdepartementet tok tak i saken slapp hun unna."}, {"field": "dominantimage", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/incoming/article1301000.ece5/ALTERNATES/w980-default/cecilie%20slapp_2"}, {"field": "dominantimagedimensions", "value": "980x551"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnail", "value": "http://content-thumbnail.cxpublic.com/content/dominantthumbnail/8c9680356cb53c18077efc30add6095839e90fbf.jpg?5988bd03"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnaildimensions", "value": "300x169"}, {"field": "heading", "value": ["Slapp unna tjeneste -adressa.no", "Kunne ikke nekte", "Departementet grep inn", "Fikk g\u00e5 hjem"]}, {"field": "id", "value": "8c9680356cb53c18077efc30add6095839e90fbf"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": ["utenriks", "innenriks", "trondheim", "E6", "midtbyen", "bybrann", "bilulykker"]}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "utenriks,innenriks,trondheim,E6,midtbyen,bybrann,bilulykker"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": ["nyheter", "trondheim"]}, {"field": "kw-classification", "value": "law-government-and-politics"}, {"field": "kw-concept", "value": ["unna tjeneste", "saken", "tape", "slapp unna", "slapp unna tjeneste", "fritak", "tjeneste", "unna", "mandag", "beskjed", "adressa", "slapp"]}, {"field": "kw-entity", "value": "sivilforsvaret"}, {"field": "kw-location", "value": "trondheim"}, {"field": "kw-pageclass", "value": "article"}, {"field": "kw-person", "value": ["knut storberget", "cecilie s\u00e6ther", "erik klomsten"]